item.title: Pi Cash on in inventory when u kill some one [HELP] PI
item.dc:creator: @runescape_sucks runescape sucks
item.description:
@runescape_sucks wrote:

[quote=“Bl3nd, post:4, topic:525730”][quote author=pawelek link=topic=644471.msg4336261#msg4336261 date=1374424777]
the compiler says error: can’t find symbol: o.getPA<>.additem<995, 50000000>;

he says he dont know the o or the dot after (). o.getPA().addItem(995, 5000000); pl0x help me it will fix i dont have to use pkp
[/quote]
The “o” should be a “c”…[/quote]

Wrong, in this case.

o.getItems().addItem(995, 5000000);
